Package: rrsimulations
Type: Package
Title: A Package to Simulate Regularized Regression Models
Version: 0.1.0
Author: David Toth
Maintainer: Alan Huebner <alan.huebner.10@nd.edu>
Description: rrsimulations is a package aimed at practioners and researchers who use lasso, ridge, and/or elastic-net models in their work. 
    It provides a set of functions that allow users to easily run simulation studies to investigate how regularized regression models behave under different covariate structures and fitting methods. 
